modules.description: This library provides low-level MP3 decoding capabilities, handling operations like file/stream initialization, ID3 tag skipping, frame-level decoding, and metadata extraction. It works with raw MP3 data through a file handle, exposing frame properties (layer, bitrate, sample rate) and supporting output formats such as interleaved PCM, float arrays, and bigarrays. It is suited for audio processing tasks requiring precise MP3 frame manipulation, format conversion, or metadata analysis, with a dedicated function to calculate file duration without full decoding.
